│ of the loop vectorizer, specifically when executing the VPlan to transform the original    │
│ loop into a vectorized one.\n\n### Analyzing `opt`'s Log\n\nThe `opt` log with             │
│ `-debug-only=loop-vectorize` provides a clear picture of the vectorization process.\n1.    │
│ The loop in the `test` function is identified as vectorizable.\n2.  A VPlan (Vectorization │
